    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those scripts developed in contexts of writing or transcribing documents, often tending toward cursive and informality and sometimes characterized by special stylization or ornamentation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
